Subject: net: ethtool: Add new power limit get and set features
Patch-mainline: v6.11-rc1
Git-commit: 30d7b6727724ce3729f2cb5b8be985d2d1931d2b
Alt-commit: 4cddb0f15ea9c62f81b4889ea69a99368cc63a86
